    <h1>Intent Data</h1>
    <p class="description">Behavioral signals — search queries, content consumption, review site visits — that reveal which prospects are <strong>actively researching a solution right now</strong>, not just loosely aware of it.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
